<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śakavaruṣaṁbhulu 1315 gunēṁṭi jaiṣṭa śukla tri
<lb n="2" break="no"/>tīyya bhudhavārānanu mēdini mallujīyyana tanaku nabhīṣṭā
<lb n="3" break="no"/>rtthasiddhigānu śrīnarasiṁhanāthuni sa<unclear>nni</unclear>di nityamunnu tiruma
<lb n="4" break="no"/>jana Apasaramaṁdu garayā Okaṭi dhūpakālamaṁdu goḍaU ni<unclear>ba</unclear>ṁ
<lb n="5" break="no"/>dhamu Okaṭi tirutōmāla Okaṭi I muṁḍu nibaṁdalunu sama
<lb n="6" break="no"/>rppiṁ<unclear>ce</unclear>nu I nibhaṁddalu tirumajjyena kālānanu garaya tēnu vallabhi
<lb n="7" break="no"/><unclear>na</unclear>ṁbhyā<unclear>ḷu</unclear>nu kūrmmanaṁbhyāḷunu kuṁcca prasādānaku vīrikē A<unclear>ru</unclear> 
<lb n="8"/>māḍalu beṭi ṭāvu padēnu goḍavu nibhaṁdānaku dupakā<supplied reason="omitted">lā</supplied>na bhaṭṭānu
<lb n="9" break="no"/>nu paṁ <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> ḍu <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> kuṁccaprasādānaku Itaniki nalu<unclear>bha</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="10"/>4 peṭenu tirumālaku kuṁcaprasādānaku nālgu māḍalu vutsukoni <unclear>dī</unclear>
<lb n="11" break="no"/>vāla guṁṭe māla peṭaṁgalāṁḍu I mālaku ga <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> ṭu paccanāyuni cēta
<lb n="12"/>gaṭu Okaṭi krayaṁkoni peṭenu I goḍavu cerigitē<unclear>ni</unclear>ku ṭana <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
